[
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "1",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069001",
        "Body":  "OH, THE LAYING-BARE of the truth!\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "10",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069010",
        "Body":  "and rebelled against their Sustainer\u0027s apostles: and so He took\n\t\t\tthem to task with a punishing grasp exceedingly severe!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "11",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069011",
        "Body":  "[And] behold: when the waters [of Noah\u0027s flood] burst beyond all\n\t\t\tlimits, it was We who caused you\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e to be borne [to\n\t\t\tsafety] in that floating ark,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "12",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069012",
        "Body":  "so that We might make all this\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e7\u003c/span\u003e a [lasting] reminder to\n\t\t\tyou all, and that every wide-awake ear might consciously take it\n\t\t\tin."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "13",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069013",
        "Body":  "Hence, [bethink yourselves of the Last Hour,] when the trumpet\n\t\t\t[of judgment] shall be sounded with a single blast,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "14",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069014",
        "Body":  "and the earth and the mountains shall be lifted up and crushed\n\t\t\twith a single stroke!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "15",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069015",
        "Body":  "And so, that which must come to pass\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e will on that Day\n\t\t\thave come to pass;"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "16",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069016",
        "Body":  "and the sky will be rent asunder\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e9\u003c/span\u003e for, frail will it\n\t\t\thave become on that Day -;"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "17",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069017",
        "Body":  "and the angels [will appear] at its ends,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e and, above\n\t\t\tthem, eight will bear aloft on that Day the throne of thy\n\t\t\tSustainer\u0027s almightiness....\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "18",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069018",
        "Body":  "On that Day you shall be brought to judgment: not [even] the most\n\t\t\thidden of your deeds will remain hidden."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "19",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069019",
        "Body":  "Now as for him whose record shall be placed in his right\n\t\t\thand,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e he will exclaim: \"Come you all! Read this my\n\t\t\trecord!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "2",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069002",
        "Body":  "How awesome that laying-bare of the truth!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "20",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069020",
        "Body":  "Behold, I did know that [one day] I would have to face my\n\t\t\taccount!\"\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "21",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069021",
        "Body":  "And so he will find himself in a happy state of life,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "22",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069022",
        "Body":  "in a lofty paradise,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "23",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069023",
        "Body":  "with its fruits within easy reach."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "24",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069024",
        "Body":  "[And all who are thus blest will be told:] \"Eat and drink with\n\t\t\tgood cheer in return for all [the good deeds] that you have sent\n\t\t\tahead in days gone by!\""
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "25",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069025",
        "Body":  "But as for him whose record shall be placed in his left\n\t\t\thand,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e he will exclaim: \"Oh, would that I had never\n\t\t\tbeen shown this my record,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "26",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069026",
        "Body":  "and neither known this my account!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "27",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069027",
        "Body":  "Oh, would that this [death of mine] had been the end of me!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "28",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069028",
        "Body":  "Of no avail to me is all that I have [ever] possessed,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "29",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069029",
        "Body":  "[and] all my power of argument has died away from me!\"\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "3",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069003",
        "Body":  "And what could make thee conceive what that laying-bare of the\n\t\t\ttruth will be?\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "30",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069030",
        "Body":  "[Thereupon the command will go forth:] \"Lay hold of him, and\n\t\t\tshackle him,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "31",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069031",
        "Body":  "and then let him enter hell,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "32",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069032",
        "Body":  "and then thrust him into a chain [of other sinners like\n\t\t\thim\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e17\u003c/span\u003e - a chain] the length whereof is seventy\n\t\t\tcubits:\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e18\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "33",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069033",
        "Body":  "for, behold, he did not believe in God, the Tremendous,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "34",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069034",
        "Body":  "and did not feel any urge\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e19\u003c/span\u003e to feed the needy:"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "35",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069035",
        "Body":  "and so, no friend has he here today,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "36",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069036",
        "Body":  "nor any food save the filth"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "37",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069037",
        "Body":  "which none but the sinners eat!\"\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e20\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "38",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069038",
        "Body":  "BUT NAY! I call to witness all that you can see,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "39",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069039",
        "Body":  "as well as all that you cannot see!\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e21\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "4",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069004",
        "Body":  "THE LIE gave [the tribes of] Thamud and \u0027Ad to [all tidings of]\n\t\t\tthat sudden calamity!\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "40",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069040",
        "Body":  "Behold, this [Qur\u0027an] is indeed the [inspired] word of a noble\n\t\t\tapostle,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "41",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069041",
        "Body":  "and is not - however little you may [be prepared to] believe it -\n\t\t\tthe word of a poet;"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "42",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069042",
        "Body":  "and neither is it - however little you may [be prepared to] take\n\t\t\tit to heart - the word of a soothsayer:"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "43",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069043",
        "Body":  "[it is] a revelation from the Sustainer of all the worlds."
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "44",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069044",
        "Body":  "Now if he [whom We have entrusted with it] had dared to attribute\n\t\t\tsome [of his own] sayings unto Us,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "45",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069045",
        "Body":  "We would indeed have seized him by his right hand,\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e22\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "46",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069046",
        "Body":  "and would indeed have cut his life-vein,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "47",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069047",
        "Body":  "and none of you could have saved him!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "48",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069048",
        "Body":  "And, verily, this [Qur\u0027an] is a reminder to all the\n\t\t\tGod-conscious.\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e23\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "49",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069049",
        "Body":  "And, behold, well do We know that among you are such as will give\n\t\t\tthe lie to it:"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "5",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069005",
        "Body":  "Now as for the Thamud - they were destroyed by a violent upheaval\n\t\t\t[of the earth];\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "50",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069050",
        "Body":  "yet, behold, this [rejection] will indeed become a source of\n\t\t\tbitter regret for all who deny the truth [of God\u0027s revelation] -"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "51",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069051",
        "Body":  "for, verily, it is truth absolute!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "52",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069052",
        "Body":  "Extol, then, the limitless glory of thy Sustainer\u0027s mighty name!"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "6",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069006",
        "Body":  "and as for the \u0027Ad - they were destroyed by a storm wind furiously\n\t\t\traging,"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "7",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069007",
        "Body":  "which He willed against them for seven nights and eight days\n\t\t\twithout cease, so that in the end thou couldst see those people\n\t\t\tlaid low [in death], as though they were so many [uprooted]\n\t\t\ttrunks of hollow palm trees:"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "8",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069008",
        "Body":  "and dost thou now see any remnant of them?"
    },
    {
        "BookCode":  "ASD",
        "SurahNumber":  "69",
        "AyahNumber":  "9",
        "Recitation":  "Alafasy_128kbps/069009",
        "Body":  "And there was Pharaoh, too, and [many of] those who lived before\n\t\t\thim, and the cities that were overthrown\u003cspan class=\u0027fn\u0027\u003e5\u003c/span\u003e - [all of\n\t\t\tthem] indulged in sin upon sin"
    }
]
